msgid ""
"Loja es reconocida a nivel sudamericano por exportar grandes talentos "
"históricos en el ámbito de la música sacra y académica."
msgstr ""
"Loja is recognized at the South American level for exporting great "
"historical talents in the field of sacred and academic music."

msgid "tu@correo.com"
msgstr "you@email.com"

msgid ""
"Se fortalece la educación musical y se crea el Conservatorio Salvador "
"Bustamante Celi."
msgstr ""
"Musical education is strengthened, and the Salvador Bustamante Celi "
"Conservatory is created."

msgid ""
"Preservando el legado sonoro y la herencia cultural de la capital musical "
"del Ecuador a través de la tecnología digital."
msgstr ""
"Preserving the sound legacy and cultural heritage of Ecuador's musical "
"capital through digital technology."

